            "title":"Primero Latino — La Salita de Washington Heights",
            "services":["Spatial Previsualization","Experiential Design","3D Rendering"],
            "date":"2025",
            "text": "For the 25th NYLFF Closing Block Party, and in collaboration with event planner Sovereign Bee, I developed the previsualization renders for Primero Latino's La Salita de Washington Heights. The nostalgic installation was inspired by Bad Bunny's La Casita Pop Up and designed to celebrate the culture and presence of the Latino community.</p><p>In addition to creating the renderings, I assisted with on-site installation and event setup, helping translate the visual concept into the final physical experience for the festival’s closing celebration.</p><p>Click <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/DPvvPxoEdwx/\" class=\"lnk-copy\">here</a> to see a glimpse of the event.",
